{"tid":739491,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【鼓舞人心】泰洞救少足故事 落實拍成荷李活電影","createTime":"2018-07-12T06:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T15:19:50.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c2845267278dcf2d15ae9cd81730fd9a5dd6f0","tid":739491,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180711/large/1531284600_71ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180711%2Flarge%2F1531284600_71ff.jpg&h=d79c1113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國清萊一支13人少年足球隊被困水浸山洞9日後奇蹟生還，噚日更全部脫險，過程緊張又曲折。有電影公司，已火速宣佈會將故事拍成電影，就連監製都落實埋，相信好快就會將事件重現觀眾眼前。<br />\n<br />\n製作公司Pure Flix Entertainment宣佈會將泰少足遇險及被救一事搬上大銀幕，並由《上帝未死》（God's Not Dead）監製主理。製作公司CEO Michael Scott表示：「我見到嘅勇敢同英雄們真係好鼓舞人心，係，呢個會成為一套戲。」佢仲話已經同過其中一啲參與拯救行動嘅潛水員傾計，又接觸過被困少年嘅家人。將來幾個星期，佢會搵編劇去寫劇本，製作費預算為3000至6000萬美金（約港幣2.3億至4.7億）。<br />\n精選娛聞，喺晒《娛果》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180711/58428348\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180711%2F58428348&d=b%2BL7yZQHkTtw9lNrjqR4f4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=7a1c4b3a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180711%2F58428348&h=45029f1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180711/58428348</a>"},{"pid":"84a3ea1df496d59973740f85d0f3fc04287da2e4","tid":739491,"uid":8867,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T06:56:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e48e74a5694bf7053ef8cd4e042c5235ebeeb1c","tid":739491,"uid":132587,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T07:02:21.000Z","msg":"叫班演員落多次去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a11e7c8bb645ce6af